<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #00466a;">Xuthority</h2>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em;">
            Hi <%= userName %>,
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            We received a request to reset your password for your <strong>Xuthority</strong> account. If you made this request, please click the button below to set a new password:
        </p>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" style="background-color: #00466a; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
                Reset Password
            </a>
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email â€” your password will remain unchanged.
        </p>

        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 10px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #aaa;">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Xuthority. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 